OL,3,CShould companies be forced to report
OL,4,Ctheir gender pay gaps?
OL,6,FJersey's government has again rejected
OL,7,Fcalls to introduce legislation forcing
OL,8,Fbusinesses to publish their gender pay
OL,9,Fgap statistics.
OL,11,FIn a scrutiny meeting on Tuesday 6
OL,12,FMay, the island's Assistant Chief
OL,13,FMinister Carina Alves said legislation
OL,14,Fof this nature would "place too much
OL,15,Fburden on businesses and entail quite
OL,16,Fa significant cost to government".
