OL,3,CShould companies be forced to report
OL,4,Ctheir gender pay gaps?
OL,6,FThe Government has since added that
OL,7,Fthis decision aligns with the goals of
OL,8,Ftheir common strategic policy, which
OL,9,Fstated they would not be overly
OL,10,Fbureaucratic and interfere too much in
OL,11,Fthe private sector.
OL,13,FWhat is the gender pay gap?
OL,15,FThe gender pay gap is the difference
OL,16,Fin average hourly earnings between men
OL,17,Fand women.
OL,19,FHowever, it is not just about men
OL,20,Fbeing paid more for the same job.
