OL,3,CShould companies be forced to report
OL,4,Ctheir gender pay gaps?
OL,6,FFactors like taking career breaks to
OL,7,Fraise children, the over-
OL,8,Frepresentation of women in lower-
OL,9,Fpaying sectors, and a hesitancy to
OL,10,Fhire women in high-earning managerial
OL,11,Fpositions also contribute.
OL,13,FIn the UK, the gender pay gap was 7%
OL,14,Fin April 2024.
OL,16,FWhat is gender pay gap reporting?
OL,18,FIn the UK, it is a legal requirement
OL,19,Ffor companies with more than 250
OL,20,Femployees to report their gender pay
OL,21,Fgap data.
