OL,3,CShould companies be forced to report
OL,4,Ctheir gender pay gaps?
OL,6,FIt is argued that this transparency
OL,7,Fmakes it easier to compare salaries,
OL,8,Fexpose inequality, and introduce
OL,9,Fmeasures that will help create change.
OL,11,FThe European Parliament also
OL,12,Fintroduced legislation in March 2023
OL,13,Fwhich forced EU companies to disclose
OL,14,Finformation that makes it easier to
OL,15,Fcompare salaries and imposes
OL,16,Fregulations if they report a gender
OL,17,Fpay gap of more than 5%.
OL,19,FHowever, neither Jersey nor Guernsey
OL,20,Fhas equivalent laws.
