OL,6,FWhat is the gender pay gap in the
OL,7,FChannel Islands?
OL,9,FWhilst Jersey's government say they
OL,10,Fhave no plans to enforce pay gap
OL,11,Freporting, they explain they are
OL,12,Fleading by example in publishing their
OL,13,Fown gender pay gap data annually.
OL,15,FStatistics Jersey also produces pay
OL,16,Fgap reports using data from income tax
OL,17,Freturns and social security
OL,18,Fcontributions.
OL,20,FIn 2024, the pay gap in Jersey was
OL,21,F7.8%.
