OL,3,CShould companies be forced to report
OL,4,Ctheir gender pay gaps?
OL,6,FThe States of Guernsey say they do not
OL,7,Fcurrently collect data that allows
OL,8,Fthem to reliably report on the gender
OL,9,Fpay gap.
OL,11,FLocal campaigners say forcing
OL,12,Fbusinesses to report pay gaps would
OL,13,Fbring greater transparency and be a
OL,14,Fcritical step towards achieving gender
OL,15,Fequality.
OL,17,FCountries in Europe have shown that
OL,18,Fthe shift can bring about change -
OL,19,FLuxembourg currently favours women
OL,20,Fwith a pay gap of -0.9% after making
OL,21,Funequal pay illegal in 2016.
