OL,3,CShould companies be forced to report
OL,4,Ctheir gender pay gaps?
OL,6,FAlex Ruddy, Chair of Jersey's
OL,7,FInstitute of Directors and co-founder
OL,8,Fof campaign group 'Mind the Gap', says
OL,9,Ftransparency is a necessary step
OL,10,Ftowards achieving equal pay, improving
OL,11,Fchildcare and maternity policies, and
OL,12,Fenabling career progression.
OL,14,F"Reporting your gender pay gap is not
OL,15,Fgoing to solve everything - it's a
OL,16,Fsmall step towards gender equality and
OL,17,Frecognising that diversity on boards
OL,18,For in businesses is a good thing", she
OL,19,Fsays.
