OL,6,F"It is a demonstration by a business
OL,7,Fof the steps they are taking to
OL,8,Faddress the gender pay gap."
OL,10,FShe adds that all female professionals
OL,11,Fwill have encountered issues relating
OL,12,Fto pay inequality, maternal leave, or
OL,13,Fcareer progression at some point.
