OL,3,CShould companies be forced to report
OL,4,Ctheir gender pay gaps?
OL,6,F"It's about ensuring that people
OL,7,Frealise that those 'career gaps' -
OL,8,Fwhen you've spent time away from work
OL,9,Fto have children - are valuable, and
OL,10,Fit doesn't belittle the professional
OL,11,Fqualifications you'd previously held
OL,12,For the work you'd undertaken to get
OL,13,Fthere."
OL,15,FMind the Gap is currently working
OL,16,Falongside the Government to provide
OL,17,Fincentives and toolkits for local
OL,18,Fbusinesses, with the hope that this
OL,19,Fwill allow them to publish their own
OL,20,Fstatistics and take the steps towards
OL,21,Fpay equality.
